{"tid":291001,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新媒體Stakk大裁員！稱員工太香港 冀攻內地","createTime":"2017-06-20T08:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T02:19:09.000Z","uid":11576,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee56fa7624fe360fb123f42fb7a54ae480e594e5","tid":291001,"uid":11576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"電訊盈科（008）主席李澤楷，去年注資千萬美元於持有《信報》的信託基金，以創辦新媒體「Stakk Factory Limited」。據消息人士向本報透露，公司<span style=\"color: red;\">上周突然不動聲息下，裁走25名員工</span>，相當於公司四分一人，被裁職位包括技術、銷售、市場等部門，當中亦包括公司技術總監。<br />\n<br />\n行政總裁勞敏琪於內部會議上指，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港用戶少，市場小，因此公司希望轉攻內地市場，認為現時員工太本土化</span></span>，因此有需要進行業組，遂作出裁員決定。至於營運總監Howard Kwong，於公司大裁員後決定自行辭職，以示不滿公司決定。<br />\n<br />\nStakk以原創視像為主打，面對全球市場，專攻年輕人市場。李澤楷當初原希望把Stakk打造成大中華Snapchat，通過有趣影片內容結合廣告來運營。目前Facebook專頁Like數67.39萬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170620&amp;guid=56852560&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170620%26guid%3D56852560%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=6TMFAya9mM%2BOk1hvvrry2wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=df17f9e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170620%26guid%3D56852560%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=268ee73a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170620&amp;guid=56852560&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dbb680e326b7b37c2b98e28fd050f7a7181619","tid":291001,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"大中華snapchat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e51bb19f0f5a3e63fea100971057b94b3243934","tid":291001,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:48:43.000Z","msg":"香港真係得樓市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 投資其他野都係玩撚完"},{"pid":"e62c918d1a5afca2526c477416378ac19cccb75e","tid":291001,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"原來間野係成哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n怪唔得間野半年無生意都可以唔執仲養返人地轉頭 個百幾個員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260cb0617dc7b05de9123ca2a4267abbffbd23f1","tid":291001,"uid":76198,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:07:35.000Z","msg":"其實小小超知唔知snapchat係咩, stakk做緊嘅同snapchat好似大纜都扯唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且大陸做類似content嘅又唔係少，做所謂大中華snapchat嘅，有冇得做都係問題，點監管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce7d6a999d7621aa17eddf9a4a24babef7d8b00","tid":291001,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"大中華snapchat應該係大陸個快手APP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b8fc18b1408ec43186dc27a7495322ec7de6e6","tid":291001,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"間野d人成日過poly做訪問<br />\n仲以為班友係poly仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f35a02c62653951341546ecee45fdc2a367686","tid":291001,"uid":123127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來間野係成哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n怪唔得間野半年無生意都可以唔執仲養返人地轉頭 個百幾個員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你見D片咁有心機執得咁靚仔，又有鬼仔鬼妹staff但又冇乜廣告就知老